Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.12,0:01:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我回家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.85,0:01:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到了没  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.22,0:01:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗唆耶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.56,0:01:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快回去回去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:57.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们每次回来\N这里的时候就只会吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.06,0:01:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  枫姥姥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  让她走掉行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.07,0:02:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关我啥事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  犬夜叉那个大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.65,0:02:18.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是因为担心他的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才会阻止打斗的说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.65,0:02:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打消念头嘛  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉吃醋不是家常便饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.26,0:02:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉的心胸太狭窄了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.47,0:02:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才会把钢牙的蠢话当真
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:42.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实他是个对自己\N毫无自信的可怜虫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也代表着他是真的喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.98,0:02:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是回去拿些药跟绷带
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就会回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.68,0:02:56.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过对犬夜叉要保密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:02:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔也该让他担心一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要快点回来喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第47话\N奈落残留的鬼蜘蛛灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落…有何贵干
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉这么敏锐  桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能没发现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且不只今天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.28,0:03:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经不下数次\N来查探我的情况了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:04:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像很在意我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.89,0:04:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落  你会在意我\N也是身不由己的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为在你心中\N鬼蜘蛛的心还强烈的残存着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.27,0:04:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.56,0:04:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.56,0:04:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.36,0:04:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要先用餐  还是先洗澡?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你这么累
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈现在就去准备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  好了  行李放下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:05:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不像是母亲和女儿的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.81,0:05:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是在外地就职的\N上班族与妻子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  这次要待几天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.16,0:05:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡个觉就要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  草太
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把绷带跟外伤药拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是床最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.11,0:05:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让他稍微担心一下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.13,0:05:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落  你会在意我\N也是身不由己的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.43,0:05:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:06:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为在你心中\N鬼蜘蛛的心还强烈的残存着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明随时都可以杀了那女人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会下不了手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是因为我奈落的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.21,0:06:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还残留着对桔梗朝思暮想的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼蜘蛛的心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.95,0:06:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼蜘蛛的心…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个卑微的盗贼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使身体无法动弹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.76,0:06:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对桔梗的非分之想却与日俱增
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后将身体献给众多的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.97,0:06:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而诞生出我奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那愚蠢人类的心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对桔梗朝思暮想的心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还残留在我奈落的身体里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.76,0:07:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗  你真是太轻视我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我奈落不是鬼蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在四魂之玉\N已大致到手的现在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼蜘蛛的心也等于无了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那团乌云是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从刚才就停在寺院上面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很不吉利耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.83,0:08:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些光是…死魂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它在吞噬着死魂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.05,0:08:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.11,0:08:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是奈落所做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.12,0:08:30.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗姑娘  您要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  马借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙打算吞尽\N这块土地所有的死魂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.51,0:08:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不能让他得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了  死魂被抽出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.02,0:09:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法师  伤口的情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还会痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经舒服多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是拜珊瑚\N你们的照顾所赐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:15.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  奈落还有着\N各式各样的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指兽郎丸和影郎丸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的…第四个分身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弟弟兽郎丸  只拥有战斗的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.57,0:10:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连奈落的命令都不服从
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算那只是傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却毫不犹豫砍下\N己方奈落的脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连奈落都难以掌控的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.08,0:10:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜伏在兽郎丸肚子里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.19,0:10:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伺机攻击的哥哥影郎丸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.82,0:10:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样非常残忍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:48.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是完全不知底细的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.59,0:10:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后不知会出现怎样的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往后非得要更加谨慎小心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:10:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不打算\N去接戈薇姑娘回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗唆耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙不在我还乐的清静咧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.01,0:11:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你不要把气氛\N搞的这么烦躁嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很累人耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.79,0:11:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真耐得住性子跟犬夜叉交往
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我深表认同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是回去拿些药跟绷带
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.13,0:11:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就会回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过对犬夜叉要保密喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.91,0:11:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔也该让他担心一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.04,0:11:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经和戈薇约定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是别说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大致上  怎么看\N都是钢牙的单相思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就不用提心吊胆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闷不做声而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.66,0:11:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像全部都是我的错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会道歉咧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇那个大浑蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是不快点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:21.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不就变成大坏蛋了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底做了什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.46,0:12:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇真的生气了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.19,0:12:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她现在在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨大的死魂虫?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.88,0:12:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬…夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好严重的伤  这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.46,0:13:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奈落的毒蜂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.86,0:13:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是奈落搞的鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算解决桔梗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不允许这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.34,0:13:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎能让奈落杀害桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.76,0:13:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗  我马上解决怪虫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这边静静等我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.07,0:13:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大怪虫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.41,0:14:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰上我算你倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.90,0:14:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.10,0:14:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有死魂\N你就无法存活了吗…桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.74,0:15:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬…夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么  你会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才要问你呢  你怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被妖怪赶来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以来这里找我帮忙的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少自负了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不知不觉中逃到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.03,0:15:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经晚上了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不把我叫起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还没睡醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.31,0:16:09.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五十年了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么  你在想什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得\N我们和五十年前一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.69,0:16:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说傻话了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.19,0:16:25.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从将你封印在此开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.33,0:16:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经就变了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.93,0:16:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们因奈落的陷阱而彼此憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被封印在\N这棵树的五十年之间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.61,0:16:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗  那么是我变了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我知道奈落\N那家伙的存在之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的确曾经恨过你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  你不是也说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.86,0:16:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的命是属于你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:16:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你的命…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是属于我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追根究底  你也和奈落一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和奈落一样?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实残留着鬼蜘蛛的心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.42,0:17:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼蜘蛛的心?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.95,0:17:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个盗贼一直\N希望我成为他的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.59,0:17:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特地指使我亲手除掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是受盗贼鬼蜘蛛\N强烈的嫉妒心驱使
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嫉妒…为了那么一点小事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  就这么点小事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.07,0:17:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而…这就是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落的体内\N还残留着鬼蜘蛛的心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.95,0:17:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说奈落对你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.85,0:17:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他根本不想承认
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.45,0:18:00.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我似乎还残留着思念这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了否定这种念头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才想要我消失的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的体内已充满了死魂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.17,0:18:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.58,0:18:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算一个人消灭奈落吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.88,0:18:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那奈落居然迷恋着你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.95,0:18:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶心至极
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.73,0:18:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.96,0:18:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉的脑袋也该冷静了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉跟桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在的这段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在怎么想都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但怎能将你交给奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.26,0:19:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能从奈落手中保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我而已不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在发什么疯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.53,0:19:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会杀了奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.26,0:19:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你不需要再战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.73,0:19:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就由我来保护
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.97,0:19:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.34,0:19:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:04.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.88,0:20:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人真是愚蠢的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.38,0:20:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以为紧紧抱着  女人就是自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.62,0:20:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.32,0:20:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到现在的你就更能了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要奈落仍有鬼蜘蛛的心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.76,0:20:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必定能趁虚而入
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时正是净化奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他从世上完全消失掉的时机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.77,0:20:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.14,0:20:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.08,0:20:41.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾纠缠在一起的命运之线
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经无法复元了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.52,0:20:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嫉妒?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.27,0:21:07.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是鬼蜘蛛那龌龊人类的心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.88,0:21:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.02,0:21:22.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个光是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.33,0:21:24.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死魂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.46,0:21:28.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗姐姐在这附近吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.55,0:21:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇…你看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.46,0:21:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉…他一直注视着我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.79,0:21:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.39,0:22:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何…你目不转睛的盯着我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:30.70,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,何不把真正重要的事物以外{\fad(500,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.04,0:22:42.18,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,全部 都舍弃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.28,0:22:49.62,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,现实 往往是如此残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.59,0:22:53.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,但每当 遇到这种时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.36,0:22:58.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要紧闭双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.10,0:23:05.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,便能看见 你的笑容{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.67,0:23:12.31,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah- 但愿从此以往
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.15,0:23:19.89,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,直到进入 沉眠的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.62,0:23:27.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,你的 那抹笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.03,0:23:35.60,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,都绝没有 消逝的瞬间{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.67,0:23:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下定决心保护桔梗的犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.91,0:23:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经无法留在他身边了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.47,0:23:54.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么想的我  再度逃回了现代
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.68,0:23:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是四魂碎片还在我手上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.21,0:23:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此非得回战国时代才行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.45,0:24:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是还给犬夜叉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.32,0:24:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切就真的结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.79,0:24:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苦恼的我  站在第一次\N遇见犬夜叉的神木之前
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.99,0:24:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.49,0:24:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想回到相遇的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.48,0:24:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬请期待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.40,0:24:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉宝典
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.81,0:25:20.91,KEYPOINT,NTP,0,0,0,,吞噬死魂的妖怪{\pos(290,291)}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.81,0:25:20.91,KEYPOINT,NTP,0,0,0,,是奈落为了消灭\N桔梗而派来出来的{\pos(270,438)}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.81,0:25:21.80,KEYPOINT,NTP,0,0,0,,巨大死魂虫{\pos(464,189)}
